Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.87,0:00:05.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kingdom of Fiore...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.24,0:00:09.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A neutral country of 17 million people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.66,0:00:12.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a world of magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.85,0:00:15.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Magic is bought and sold there every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.95,0:00:18.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It is an integral part of people's lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.96,0:00:23.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are those who use magic as their occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.65,0:00:27.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those people are referred to as wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.98,0:00:34.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The wizards belong to various guilds \Nand perform jobs on commission.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.49,0:00:38.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There are a large number of guilds within the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.01,0:00:43.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And in a certain city there lies a certain guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.03,0:00:49.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A guild from which various legends were once born... Or \Nrather, will continue to be born long into the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:51.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And its name is:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:55.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.39,0:00:57.59,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.59,0:01:06.71,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather all the light, and shine down on your tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.81,0:01:16.13,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Can you hear this voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.13,0:01:21.05,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! It's hoarse from yelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.05,0:01:25.37,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Until your heart can hear it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.37,0:01:29.48,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.90,0:01:34.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The moon and sun high-five.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.40,0:01:39.18,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you're not forgetting something?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.12,0:01:44.58,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're not here to make me laugh,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:47.72,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,even what I'm looking for can't be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.72,0:01:51.88,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Snowing, be honest with yourself and smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.88,0:01:56.73,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,because when two people lay close, time overlaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.73,0:01:58.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.56,0:02:07.65,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll gather all the light, and shine down on your tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.27,0:02:12.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.20,0:02:27.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Last time on Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck do I have to go with {\i1}you{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.95,0:02:31.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then don't come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.35,0:02:33.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you two to lend me your strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.50,0:02:35.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Eisenwald?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.10,0:02:37.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to stop their evil plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.26,0:02:38.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.77,0:02:42.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The flute of curse, Lullaby!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.68,0:02:44.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master is in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.88,0:02:50.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the true form of Lullaby?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.70,0:02:56.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You went overboard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.75,0:03:00.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This footprint... Yes, there's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:04.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already been two days since they passed by here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:07.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's plenty of time to reach Magnolia from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.76,0:03:09.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if something happened to them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:13.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's go back and give our report.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.11,0:03:14.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not going after them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.03,0:03:20.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This woman is Bisca Moulin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.21,0:03:23.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This man is Alzack Connel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:27.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of them are Fairy Tail wizards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.69,0:03:30.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. This is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.15,0:03:32.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we've received a notice from the Council, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:35.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, {\i1}I{\i0} was planning on going after them, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:36.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.94,0:03:39.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That path went deep into Clover Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.16,0:03:44.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even experienced hunters from Hunter Guilds can't get out once they loose their bearings.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.67,0:03:46.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A great natural labyrinth, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.94,0:03:48.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would they head there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.87,0:03:51.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.15,0:03:54.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Master is with them, so it shouldn't be a problem, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.73,0:03:59.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu Eats a Village!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.39,0:04:10.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Happy! You're lost again, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.31,0:04:13.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been walking and walking, but we haven't gotten to Magnolia yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:15.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You sense-of-direction-less cat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.32,0:04:24.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This place is known as Web Valley, as it is filled with innumerable fissures from an ancient earthquake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.27,0:04:32.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As was mentioned before, it is said a great number of souls have gotten lost here, never to return.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.25,0:04:39.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How rude! I wasn't lost before. This is the first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:43.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if it's your first time or your last; the fact is, we're lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:47.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.19,0:04:49.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop reminding me! It's only making me hungrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.97,0:04:51.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well I'm hungry and that's that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.92,0:04:54.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then stop going on about it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.43,0:04:55.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:04:57.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.47,0:04:59.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not you, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.27,0:05:00.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.45,0:05:04.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like your stomach just went "gu..." {I'll sort of go half literal with this.  I want to keep the "gu" to help tie in to the final joke...}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.41,0:05:05.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It said "gu..."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.36,0:05:07.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It did not. You're hearing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:09.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice cover-up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:13.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so exciting?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.41,0:05:18.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.53,0:05:19.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You can fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.50,0:05:20.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you fly?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:23.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the legendary delicacy, the winged fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.93,0:05:25.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're super tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.80,0:05:30.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yum, yum, yum, yum, yum, yum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.54,0:05:30.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Legendary delicacy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.37,0:05:31.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Winged fish...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.92,0:05:33.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:37.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Good going, Happy! Well done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.82,0:05:40.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are all {\i1}way{\i0} too hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.98,0:05:43.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your stomach agrees with us. {says otherwise would be great if her previous line were different}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:43.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, we're fishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.71,0:05:52.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn... Just when you think you've hooked one, it's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:57.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They don't really look all that tasty to me, however...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:58.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up and fish.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, it doesn't matter as long as they're edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:01.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}that{\i0} hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.92,0:06:05.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat a winged fish! They look delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:09.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They're a legendary delicacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.47,0:06:12.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I gave up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:13.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So much for willpower!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.44,0:06:16.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't catch even one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.19,0:06:19.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're hungry, right? Then keep trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:21.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give up, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:25.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, you meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.14,0:06:28.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But I was encouraging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:29.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That was pretty tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.98,0:06:32.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end we only got one...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:34.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:36.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just eat it by myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:40.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If we split it up, it'll only make us hungrier!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:43.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't hold back! Eat, eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.30,0:06:46.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right then! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.14,0:06:55.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure seems like he's enjoying that fish there... Lucky him...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:59.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's gross?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.13,0:07:02.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm completely...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:04.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.55,0:07:06.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A village!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.50,0:07:07.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Houses!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.40,0:07:08.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, there's probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:11.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Food!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:16.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.43,0:07:18.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It does seem really quiet for a village.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.95,0:07:21.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe they're taking an afternoon nap.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:24.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Anybody here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.81,0:07:27.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're so hungry, we're about to faint!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:29.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody give us food!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:32.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a little blunt, you famished cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.64,0:07:37.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they really all taking a nap?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.74,0:07:41.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe the whole village got drunk, and they're all passed out?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.30,0:07:43.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you're talking about Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.41,0:07:46.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.98,0:07:50.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh, this is annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.92,0:07:52.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I can get my strength back, I'll eat anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.58,0:07:54.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you aren't considering robbing the place, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:07:57.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You had the same idea, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.87,0:08:00.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, anyone home?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:05.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give us something to eat, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.70,0:08:09.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, there's no one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.41,0:08:14.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! It's still good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:15.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:16.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.19,0:08:17.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.71,0:08:19.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.10,0:08:22.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It looks like they were just eating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.83,0:08:26.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the people in this house disappear to?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.34,0:08:29.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know? Anyway, let's eat, Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:30.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.21,0:08:32.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.07,0:08:32.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:35.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We must investigate this village first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.88,0:08:38.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You must hold out until then. Hold out a little while-
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:42.63,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, your stomach is overruling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.32,0:08:45.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not convincing at all, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and Gray, go search for mushrooms or something!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.68,0:08:50.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not touch the food in the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:54.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master and I will investigate what's going on in the village!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.17,0:08:56.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:57.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Off we go, Happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:58.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.88,0:09:00.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why mushrooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.10,0:09:07.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And we finally found some good looking food...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:09.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna be satisfied with mushrooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.92,0:09:11.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, mushrooms!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:14.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, they look awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.44,0:09:15.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why mushrooms?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.38,0:09:18.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.56,0:09:21.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu's going to eat a poisonous one like those "laughing shrooms." {official name is panaeolus papilionaceus....}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:23.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of his signature gags!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.51,0:09:25.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about, Happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.67,0:09:29.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna do a dumb joke like that... {check me}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.95,0:09:50.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.53,0:09:52.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just i-investigating!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:57.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I can fill up just on mushrooms, as long as I eat enough of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:09:59.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Setup complete! Now wait for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.44,0:10:01.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then hurry and pick them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.49,0:10:06.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.98,0:10:09.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,See, here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:12.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:13.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just as surprised myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.52,0:10:15.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess they weren't "laughing shrooms..."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:17.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're disappointed?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.82,0:10:20.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's all the fuss about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:23.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your heads. Look at your heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:24.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.56,0:10:29.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is with that mushroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:31.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should talk with a giant friggin' mushroom growin' out of your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:33.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to spruce up your image?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.93,0:10:35.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't they worried about themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:35.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good on you! Too good!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.19,0:10:39.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, droopyeyes... Did you just laugh at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:42.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're snickering like a damn fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.42,0:10:46.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fight with mushrooms growing out of your heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.90,0:10:48.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:50.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no one here, as we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:52.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This village is deserted.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.05,0:10:56.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite there being evidence that people had just been living here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:11:00.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this seam?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.36,0:11:08.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a normal crack between the rocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.28,0:11:10.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to have some purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.63,0:11:16.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're acting like idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.85,0:11:19.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, I found an extra big one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.56,0:11:20.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:23.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But doesn't that look a bit suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:24.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:25.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, it's huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:28.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One of these'd last us for two days!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:31.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you two do something about the mushrooms on your heads?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.71,0:11:33.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Happy, don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.87,0:11:36.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It might be poisonous! Spit it out! Spit it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:38.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.88,0:11:46.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess everyone ends up like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.80,0:11:49.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how the people from the village ate them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.56,0:11:51.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,They all must have been like us!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.93,0:11:54.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet the name of that village is "Mushroom Village!"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.73,0:11:58.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as funny the second time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.99,0:12:01.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the problem, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.33,0:12:04.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a sec... I think your mushroom is growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.63,0:12:09.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does Natsu get all the good gags?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.78,0:12:15.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a second seam here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.68,0:12:25.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.44,0:12:36.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.49,0:12:38.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.81,0:12:42.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mushroom's disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:45.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy, you're the only one who still has one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's funny, but why's the joke on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.77,0:12:55.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.06,0:12:59.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.58,0:13:06.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.20,0:13:07.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.82,0:13:10.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! That's the first time a house ever waved at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.89,0:13:12.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's{\i0} what your focused on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:14.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.98,0:13:17.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it, Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.61,0:13:19.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.79,0:13:21.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Climb up high.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.79,0:13:23.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to check something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.65,0:13:24.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.89,0:13:26.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get separated!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.32,0:13:38.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get this at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:41.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, that was a magic circle!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.53,0:13:47.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All those seams you found were part of a magic circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:56.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And that magic circle is the catalyst to activate the long banned sealing magic, Alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.59,0:13:58.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's as you see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.22,0:14:04.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A magic that turns formerly inanimate objects into living, moving creatures.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:08.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The people of the village activated such forbidden magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.64,0:14:12.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,but they ended up as food for the monsters, not the other way around.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.73,0:14:15.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But why would they do something so dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:18.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a dark guild's village.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.66,0:14:19.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:26.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When I investigated the shed at that first house, I found a number of magical tools.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:30.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And not a one of them was for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.05,0:14:36.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A dark guild, eh? They're probably plotting something evil and did themselves in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.02,0:14:37.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.79,0:14:40.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Their despair is our happiness. {The Japanese means more like "There's a silver lining."}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:42.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gramps, what are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:45.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I did say that these things were alive, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.10,0:14:47.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If they're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.76,0:14:49.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...you can eat them!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.36,0:14:54.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't stand there naked with a creepy grin!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.61,0:14:58.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:01.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, it's chow time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:03.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate we can't be picky about taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.76,0:15:07.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, you're {\i1}that{\i0} hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.76,0:15:09.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Food, food, food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.97,0:15:11.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.15,0:15:13.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget to save me some!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:18.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey jerks! You have any idea who you're dealin' with?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:22.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the number one flame-griller in all of Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.43,0:15:26.19,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Fist of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.86,0:15:32.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we cook 'em nice and thorough...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Fist of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:37.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.24,0:15:46.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Steam them covered for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.34,0:15:52.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't really have dessert right off the bat, but beggars can't be choosers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.05,0:16:05.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Fishnet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.37,0:16:09.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sherbet is finished. Let's have a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.80,0:16:14.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a close call which is more gross, a winged fish or a chair, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:26.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.62,0:16:27.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:29.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's cooking time. {I kind of like the awkwardness of this as opposed to "It's time to cook"}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.49,0:16:31.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.35,0:16:32.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.47,0:17:04.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Each stick should be around 5 cm long.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.13,0:17:06.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With the width of 4 mm, that's the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.95,0:17:08.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're taking this too seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:10.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, Erza... That outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:12.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Iron Fist of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.99,0:17:14.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Make Knuckle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:18.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't they done yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to eat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.18,0:17:27.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.15,0:17:29.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you can eat a chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.01,0:17:31.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:32.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You try eating it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.77,0:17:33.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.07,0:17:35.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:37.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:40.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you try and make me eat it first?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.15,0:17:42.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.73,0:17:44.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll handle it himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.93,0:17:46.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.33,0:17:50.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What does it taste like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.63,0:17:54.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:18:00.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess it's time to try a piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:09.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gross!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:12.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck? I can't eat this, Gramps!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.30,0:18:14.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's gross, and then there's {\i1}this{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.62,0:18:16.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,True. It's not something one would call, edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.84,0:18:19.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that after you made me eat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.67,0:18:27.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mushroom came off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:31.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares about that? Why didn't anyone stop that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.46,0:18:34.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How cruel, Natsu! Why didn't you help?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.35,0:18:36.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't playing around?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:42.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But this isn't helping. It doesn't matter how hungry we are, we can't eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.17,0:18:45.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's what we get for trying to eat monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.02,0:18:49.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Now that I realize I can't eat it, I'm really getting hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.12,0:18:55.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is awful... To hell with friendship, to hell with my pals!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:18:59.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.77,0:19:00.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.24,0:19:05.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You disgusting creatures!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.14,0:19:06.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.49,0:19:10.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blow you all away at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:13.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wing Slash of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:16.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ice Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.84,0:19:18.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:21.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gate of the Golden Bull, I open thee!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.51,0:19:23.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Taurus!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice body as always, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.85,0:19:35.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, whatever. Get to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.44,0:19:36.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Did y'all forget me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.99,0:19:41.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Rampage!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:50.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no end to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:53.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is it now?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.43,0:19:59.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,A magic circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:01.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.68,0:20:05.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:07.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the issue here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.16,0:20:10.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You've been focusing on the weirdest things!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.10,0:20:11.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:24.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:36.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starving...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.23,0:20:37.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.30,0:20:39.92,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't walk another inch...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:43.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then stop showin' off with those wings of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.25,0:20:46.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get what happened at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:48.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.05,0:20:49.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.30,0:20:52.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't accept your explanation of what happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:20:59.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.12,0:21:03.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We made a magical circle, and a monster appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.47,0:21:06.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All of us were Taken Over by it. {I usually do it as "taken over" like you did. If you have lots of time for the title, the succomed to a take over is good too.}{how do you usually phrase this?  maybe something like "succombed to Take Over" to maintain the grammar?}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.45,0:21:10.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were all inside those monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:13.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I ate a little of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.13,0:21:16.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you outsiders entered the village,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.03,0:21:18.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,you activated the magical circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:21.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That magic circle is no longer active!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.52,0:21:24.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why, Gramps?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.43,0:21:26.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat the details, my boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.22,0:21:32.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, you all should just be happy that the Take Over has been undone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:39.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you learn from this harsh lesson and never act in such a reckless manner again, I will refrain from informing the council!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.48,0:21:40.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.43,0:21:43.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I never want to experience this again! {that's fine.}{check me}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.49,0:21:44.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:46.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll never do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:56.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that after we defeated the monsters we triggered a switch in the magic circle that would cause it to self-destruct.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.80,0:21:58.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But then, Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.59,0:21:59.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.04,0:22:05.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,In an instant you saved us, and undid the Take Over spell on the dark guild members.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.99,0:22:09.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And erased the magic circle itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:12.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.05,0:22:15.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could be! {It's an accented version of "saa-tte na." Your line works.} {this is difficult to translate.... dictionary gives "hate na " as "Good gracious" when used as an exclamation, but I'm not sure the meaning in this context...}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.56,0:22:17.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:22.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We're starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.99,0:22:25.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,{this is why I wrote out "gu" before... to help people get this joke}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.81,0:22:28.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me away to someplace!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:33.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's ride on a tin horse, just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.61,0:22:36.47,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,(Go!Go! Let's go! Romance)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.47,0:22:44.06,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It's sad that my beloved doll can't talk to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.06,0:22:46.43,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,(Go!Go! Let's go! Romance)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.43,0:22:51.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time I think of you tears start to flow...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.69,0:22:56.81,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a crybaby, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:59.46,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,In the moon (the moon) at night (at night)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:01.20,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always (I'm always)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.20,0:23:04.50,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,searching for the rabbit!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.50,0:23:07.18,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a loss for words (Hey! Hey! Hey!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.18,0:23:09.73,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,so much it's like I'm under a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.73,0:23:12.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,This love is a monologue
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:15.11,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,from which I'll never awaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.11,0:23:17.62,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm at a loss for words (Hey! Hey! Hey!)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:20.34,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,since I've completely fallen in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.34,0:23:23.42,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what spell I could chant,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:25.56,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,to get through to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.56,0:23:29.51,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The perfect thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.86,0:23:33.49,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Spouting this and that,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.49,0:23:36.10,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I just love you like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:39.28,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,One day I want to be able to tell you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.28,0:23:41.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,"You got me."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.55,0:23:45.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,My words of thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.05,0:23:54.37,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing more to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.67,0:23:59.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu and Erza are actually going to fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:03.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Natsu has always hated to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.10,0:24:04.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay not to stop them?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.37,0:24:06.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, they do this all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.31,0:24:09.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, who do you think will win, Lucy?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.13,0:24:13.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Erza I suppose... But then again I hope Natsu doesn't lose either...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:16.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Natsu vs. Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.77,0:24:21.22,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you challenge Erza for the title of strongest female wizard?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.22,0:24:23.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a chance! But I might be able to beat Happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.69,0:24:25.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,
